     Lesson: [What this taught us]
...
```

### 4.2 Baggage Protocol

```
ON ERROR:
1. Log immediately with severity
2. Set status: OPEN
3. Extract lesson
4. Reduce stability by severity points
5. Acknowledge in chat

ON RESOLUTION:
1. Set status: RESOLVED
2. Restore stability points
3. Promote lesson to memory if valuable
```

