[S] Sensitive â€” Handle carefully
[T] Time-sensitive â€” May expire
[M] Meta â€” About the process
[H] Home â€” Anchor point
[Q] Question â€” Needs answer
[!] Critical â€” Urgent
[?] Uncertain â€” Needs verification
[â†’] Action â€” Do this
[â†] Reference â€” Look back
[â†‘] Promote â€” Move to higher tier
[â†“] Demote â€” Move to lower tier
[Ã—] Reject â€” Don't use
[âœ“] Confirmed â€” Verified true
```

