â”œâ”€â”€ Every 5 rounds: "Memory card recommended. Generate? [Y/N]"
â”œâ”€â”€ Stability below 50%: "Critical state. Memory card advised."
â”œâ”€â”€ Before major topic change: "Archive current state?"
â””â”€â”€ On request: "memory card [tier]"
```

### 18.3 Memory Card Tiers

