## What You Now Have:

1. **PART A:** The complete system prompt (copy-paste ready)
2. **PART B:** User guide (how to use it)
3. **PART C:** Memory card templates (all three tiers)
4. **PART D:** Distribution package (Discord, GitHub, Reddit, Twitter)

## Key Innovations in This Version:

| Feature | What Changed |
|---------|--------------|
| Canvas-First | WORKSPACE at top for all real content |
| Chat Minimal | Just tags and pointers, not content |
| Memory Cards | 3-tier backup and transfer system |
| Tag Alignment | Chat prints sync strings for AI |
| Auto-Prompts | Memory card reminder every 5 rounds |
| Load Protocol | Boot fresh, paste card, continue |

## The Architecture Summary:

```
USER â†’ [Chat Input]
         â†“
      NEXUS reads Canvas state
         â†“
      Processes input
         â†“
      Updates Canvas WORKSPACE (full answer)
      Updates Canvas STATE SECTIONS (if needed)
         â†“
      Chat gets: brief ack + tags + pointer
         â†“
USER â† [Looks at Canvas for real content]
```

